name: Sifo-Dyas%27_father
content:
A human male was the father of the Jedi Master Sifo-Dyas. He lived on the planet Minashee. When his son was found to be Force-sensitive, he gave him to the Jedi Order to be trained as a Jedi. When the Jedi Initiate, Dooku sent a holocomm to his sister Jenza, he mentioned that Sifo-Dyas' father worked as a fisherman.
Sifo-Dyas' father was mentioned by the audiodrama Dooku: Jedi Lost, authored by Cavan Scott and published in 2019.
